'From Squeak 2.3 beta of Nov 25, 1998 on 21 December 1998 at 11:21:30 am'!"Change Set:		DefaultTransitionDate:			21 December 1998Author:			Dan IngallsMakes #none be the default for transitions, and installs the showProjectZoom preference."!!BookMorph methodsFor: 'navigation' stamp: 'di 12/21/1998 11:15'!transitionSpecFor: aMorph	^ aMorph valueOfProperty: #transitionSpec  " check for special propety"		ifAbsent: [Array with: 'camera'  " ... otherwise this is the default"						with: #none						with: #none]! !!TransitionMorph class methodsFor: 'available effects' stamp: 'di 12/21/1998 11:14'!allEffects	^ #(none		slideOver slideBoth slideAway slideBorder pageForward pageBack 		zoomFrame zoom		dissolve)! !"Postscript:Install the project zoom preference."Preferences setPreference: #showProjectZoom toValue: false.Preferences initializeHelpMessages.!